PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2001, NO. 04, HORSESHOE SLOUGH HABITAT PROTECTION AREA, Y.T. ) - which prohibits entry into certain areas of the Yukon for the purposes of prospecting or staking mineral claims, to ensure protection of the Horseshoe Slough Habitat Protection Area.

precis:
Enactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON
TERRITORY (2001, NO. 04, HORSESHOE SLOUGH HABITAT PROTECTION AREA, Y.T. ) -
which prohibits entry into certain areas of the Yukon for the purposes of
prospecting or staking mineral claims, to ensure protection of the
Horseshoe Slough Habitat Protection Area.
